author: Shelley Ng
title: Turkish Airlines flight from Istanbul to San Francisco making emergency landing in Warsaw, Poland - @airlivenet
text: BREAKING Turkish Airlines #TK79 from Istanbul to San Francisco is declaring an emergency. Live: UPDATE #TK79 diverted to Warsaw runway 33 & stand 66 due to incident regarding suspicious hand baggage of two passengers. UPDATE EMERGENCY Turkish Airlines #TK79 to San Francisco is descending over Poland. Live: http://t.co/EWu03CPhy3 pic.twitter.com/hc3Ju4KMWC
